don't want to do the door knocking, the sales. They just want to implement. They need a domain expert.":[99,99],"#messy_problem: Cultural - organisations don't understand what AI is. they struggle to utilize it appropriately":[100,100],"#messy_problem: Cyber Risk - Clients often don't understand just how vulnerable their data is. it only takes a few prompts and he can hack into an LLM and get the data.":[101,101],"#new_contact: Peter Kearney (CFO). he is 80, ex-SAS from Cold War. He is well connected. His wife is involved with the Anglican church.":[102,102],"#action_item: Confirm if going to Thursday Business Show and Defense Show with Peter":[103,103],"#action_item: Read Anthony's papers.":[104,104],"#action_item: potentially write a paper in collaboration with Anthony":[105,105]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#key_language","#messy_problem","#new_contact","#action_item"]},"task_lines":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"ycxqw1","at":1762133976581}},"smart_blocks:docs/Stakeholder Engagment/C2 - Anthony Autore/C2 - Anthony Call Notes.md##Phase 1: Frame the Call#{1}": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07352266,0.01486506,0.0511636,-0.10071697,-0.06120602,-0.02521964,0.01783873,0.07148453,0.01212253,-0.06781439,0.01477582,-0.00196372,-0.02198013,0.0150857,-0.01383839,0.01576637,-0.03799081,-0.00401849,0.01601799,0.03571559,0.0601381,-0.02119509,0.00325841,0.01143638,0.02779541,-0.00057999,0.00088006,-0.03341364,-0.0362769,-0.22168687,-0.02309974,0.06044422,0.0505892,0.00508543,-0.00122777,0.06417367,-0.02148514,0.05184164,-0.01213513,0.08480591,0.02125656,-0.00180744,-0.02790084,-0.02619674,-0.01286102,-0.06743999,0.03346425,0.00697299,-0.02006817,-0.01657117,0.00660253,0.02210572,0.01044333,-0.04918614,-0.00382576,-0.03199441,0.07967205,0.05385276,-0.00097014,0.02579859,0.01417507,0.00835897,-0.22549398,0.13446371,0.01751835,-0.01388237,-0.00218884,-0.02636334,-0.05236426,0.0763108,-0.07069621,0.00346288,-0.04834659,0.03320671,0.03391289,-0.021